<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness=
.com/click/32262470.263416/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9ibGFja3Jv=
Y2stbXNjaS1mYWNlLWNvbmdyZXNzaW9uYWwtcHJvYmVzLWZvci1mYWNpbGl0YXRpbmctY2hpbmE=
