eds to purchase luxury goods including sports cars, watches, and a 555-cara=
t black diamond known as =E2=80=98The Enigma=E2=80=99 =E2=80=93 reportedly =
the largest black diamond in the world.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">According to the SEC=E2=80=99s complaint, Hear=
t began marketing Hex in 2018, claiming it was the first high-yield =E2=80=
=9Cblockchain certificate of deposit,=E2=80=9D and began promoting Hex toke=
ns as an investment designed to make people =E2=80=9Crich.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</=
p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is a lot going on in <a href=3D"https://=
link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32262470.263416/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjL=
mdvdi9maWxlcy9saXRpZ2F0aW9uL2NvbXBsYWludHMvMjAyMy9jb21wLXByMjAyMy0xNDMucGRm=
